  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL16">
<l>cūtaṉāyk kaḷva ṉākit tūrttarō ṭicainta kālam</l>
<l>mātarār kayaṟka ṇeṉṉum valaiyuḷpaṭ ṭaḻuntu vēṉaip</l>
<l>pōtarē yeṉṟu collip puntiyiṟ pukuntu taṉpā</l>
<l>lātaram peruka vaitta vaḻakaṉū raraṅka maṉṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Raṅgam is the town of the Handsome [Lord],</l>
<l>Who said, ‘Come!’,</l>
<l>entered [my] mind,</l>
<l>and fostered a love for Him</l>
<l rend="indent">in me who am sinking</l>
<l rend="indent">being caught in the nets that are the kayal-fish[-like] eyes of women</l>
<l rend="indent">at a time when [I], a cunning person and a thief,</l>
<l rend="indent">moved with wicked people, is it not?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
